  "title": "ARCHITECTURAL ASSOCIATE",
  "description": "<p>1) Possess a recognised Architectural degree and preferably a Qualified Person registered with the Singapore Board of Architects and with Green Mark certification for Architect.<br /></p><p>2) Minimum 3 years relevant experience.<br /></p><p>3) Experience in handling projects from concept to construction.<br /></p><p>4) Liaise with consultants on matters of design & technical co-ordination site issues.<br /></p><p>5) Work closely with the project team in the co-ordination, organization & preparation of construction documents & drawings.<br /></p><p>6) Good interpersonal skills and the ability to work independently or within a team in a proactive environment.<br /></p><p>7) Contract administration.<br /></p><p>8) Be familiar with prevailing regulations and codes governing construction and architectural practice.<br /></p><p>9) AutoCad and BIM knowledge will be an advantage.</p>",
